---
import Container from "../../primitives/Container.astro";
---
<section class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="integrated-intro-title">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why integrated systems</p>
      <h2 id="integrated-intro-title" class="fluid-h2 mt-3">Complex infrastructure requires more than standalone components.</h2>
      <p class="fluid-lead mt-5 text-muted">
        Empereal designs and delivers integrated systems that combine multiple generation and storage technologies into unified solutions optimised for specific site conditions, load profiles, and regulatory environments. From nearly net-zero off-grid luxury resorts to industrial facilities requiring 24/7 power and process water, Empereal provides complete system integration — design, EPC, commissioning, and long-term O&amp;M — from a single engineering partner.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
